{
  "stem": "12882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And one evening, one of these bunch of SS characters from the Gestapo appeared, and my brother played.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it infuriated them so much that they took the piano, rolled it out on the porch, and then threw it overboard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now, if you ever have heard the clatter and the terrible sound of a breaking piano, breaking up or something, you never forget it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I still have-- what should I say-- strange feelings when a piano is shifted on stage and one of the wheels comes close to the edge of the stage.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everywhere beating and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then two nights later, another SS guy appears, an officer, who always came and his-- my brother played for him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, where's your piano?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, you see, in normal times, you say, they-- they have done that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you're going to say that the SS has rolled it out on this-- on the porch and [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think it was still lying there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, next day they brought a new Steinway grand because he wanted to hear my brother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody ever touched that piano again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One of the situation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Another situation just to tell you what one went through, the former maid of us had brought us some sugar, and we knew very-- very well sugar was not for everybody.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we put it into a bowl which said 'salt' on top.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then a Gestapo came and beat us up and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And force my brother to eat this bowl of salt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Luckily enough, it was sugar, which was difficult enough.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But imagine with salt, what that would do to your insides.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They found a pair of boots.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
